</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="105" pageNumber="384" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="105.[1401,2609,291,917]" pageId="105" pageNumber="384">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1403,1537,649,678]" pageId="105" pageNumber="384">Breeding.</emphasis>
Pregnant and lactating Broad-faced Deermice have been caught in June-August.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1402,2409,728,757]" pageId="105" pageNumber="384" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="105.[1401,2609,291,917]" box="[1402,2409,728,757]" pageId="105" pageNumber="384">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1402,1637,728,757]" pageId="105" pageNumber="384">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Broad-faced Deermouse is presumably nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
